<!-- Initiative Links -->
<div class="container initBdr">
  <h2 class="initHead">Initiatives</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap1">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/ECC.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Support at Pre-School level (Early Childhood Care and Education)</h3>
          <p>Support has been provided for the efforts of State Govt in providing Pre-school education in schools of up to 2 years duration..</p>
          <a href="early_childhood.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap2">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/padhe-bharat.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Padhe Bharat Badhe Bharat</h3>
          <p>Padhe Bharat Badhe Bharat is being implemented under the aegis of the Sarva Shiksha Abhiyan in 2014 to ensure quality at the foundational years of schooling i.e., classes I & II.</p>
          <a href="http://mhrd.gov.in/sites/upload_files/mhrd/files/document-reports/Padhe-Bharat-Badhe-Bharat.pdf" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More" target="_blank">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap3">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/libraray.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Library grant for promoting reading habits</h3>
          <p>In order to complement the activities under Padhe Bharat Badhe Bharat and inculcate the reading habits among students of all ages, strengthening of school libraries is being undertaken including provision of books.</p>
          <a href="library.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap4">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/sports.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Sports and Physical Education</h3>
          <p>Sports in schools have immense benefits for both children and for educational systems. Sports have the potential to make distinctive contributions to the development of children’s fundamental movement skills and physical competences..</p>
          <a href="sports.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap5">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/rangotsav.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Experiential Learning (Rangotsav)</h3>
          <p>For the promotion of experiential learning and joyful learning, various activities are organized for both students and teachers. Some of the major activities under taken are Kala Utsav; Role Play Competition.</p>
          <a href="rangotsav.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap6">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/children_special.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Inclusive Education for Children with Special Needs</h3>
          <p>Support has been provided for various student oriented activities which include identification and assessment of Children with Special Needs (CWSN), provision of aids, appliances..</p>
          <a href="inclusive.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/kgbv.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Kasturba Gandhi Balika Vidyalaya (KGBV)</h3>
          <p>Bridging gender and social category gaps at all levels of school education is one of the major objectives of the Samagra Shiksha. Consequently, to encourage the participation of girls..</p>
          <a href="kgbv.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap7">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/youth-club.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Constitution of Youth Club and Eco Club</h3>
          <p>Youth clubs in schools are an instrument to develop life skills, build self-esteem, develop self-confidence and resilience and counter negative emotions of stress, shame and fear.</p>
          <a href="youth.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap1">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/self-defence.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Self Defence Training (RAKSHA)</h3>
          <p>Keeping in view, the rising number of crimes against girls in the country, it is important to provide self-defence training to them in the schools to ensure their safety and security.</p>
          <a href="raksha.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap2">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/school-sefety.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>School Safety</h3>
          <p>Children have right to live with dignity and have access to education in an environment that is safe protective and conducive to growth & development.</p>
          <a href="safety.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap3">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/vocational.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Vocational Education</h3>
          <p>The scheme seeks to integrate vocational education with general academic education with an aim to prepare educated, employable and competitive human resource for various sectors of the economy and the global market.</p>
          <a href="vocational.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap4">
        <div class="picRT"><img src="images/tt.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initContRT">
          <h3>Integrated Teacher Training Programme (Elementary level)</h3>
          <p>In-service teacher and teacher educators training have been an integral part of erstwhile Schemes of SSA, RMSA and CSSTE.</p>
          <a href="integrated.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap5">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/nas.jpg" width="270" height="241" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>School Based Assessment (SBA)</h3>
          <p>Preparations for NAS 2020 (Pre NAS 2020) interventions have been initiated to reach out to all the districts of different States and UTs.</p>
          <a href="sba.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 init_marTop1">
      <div class="init_wrap6">
        <div class="pic"><img src="images/sv.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="initCont">
          <h3>Swachh Vidyalaya</h3>
          <p>The Swachh Vidyalaya Initiative started with the construction of toilets, then moved to the maintenance of toilets and activities such as hand washing ..</p>
          <a href="swachh.html" class="btn btn-default" title="Know More">Know More</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- /Initiative Links -->
<!-- Red Bg Links -->
<div class="container-fluid redBG">
  <div class="container traparentBG">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
        <div class="cont first bdrRT">
          <h3>Shaala Siddhi</h3>
          <p>The programme envisions reaching 1.6 million schools in the country through a compressive system of school evaluation.</p>
          <a href="http://shaalasiddhi.niepa.ac.in/" title="know more..." target="_blank">know more...</a> </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
        <div class="cont bdrRT">
          <h3>NAS &amp; SAS, Learning Outcomes</h3>
          <p>To monitor improvement in childrens learning levels and to periodically assess the health of the government education system as a whole.</p>
          <a href="http://www.ncert.nic.in/programmes/NAS/NAS.html" title="know more..." target="_blank">know more...</a> </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
        <div class="cont bdrRT first1 topMar1">
          <h3>Training of Untrained Teachers (NIOS)</h3>
          <p>The programme has been developed by the Academic Department, NIOS on the initiative of MHRD, Govt. of India, keeping in view the NCF 2005, RTE 2009 and NCFTE 2010.</p>
          <a href="http://dled.nios.ac.in/" title="know more..." target="_blank">know more...</a> </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
        <div class="cont topMar1">
          <h3>School Leadership and Management</h3>
          <p>National Centre for School Leadership has been established to empower school leaders with knowledge, skills and attitudes to transform schools.</p>
          <a href="http://pslm.niepa.ac.in/" title="School Leadership and Management" target="_blank">know more...</a> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- /Red Bg Links -->
